            i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
            .content
              | Social media can be a great place to find information about things 
              | that just happened or are currently taking place.

          h5.ui.header
            i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
            .content
              | When you come across breaking news on your timeline, itâ€™s 
