              | Is this article a news piece or an opinion piece?
              
          h5.ui.header
            i.circle.bullet.blue.icon
            .content
              | Does the article mention where or from whom the author got the 
              | information?
              
          h5.ui.header
            i.circle.bullet.blue.icon
            .content
